reviewText:
I didn't realise I could get a party/fuel... I spent 2 hours grinding monsters at the first ghost section...

10/10 Would Grind Again..

In all seriousness this is one of the best RPGVXACE games to come out in a while. The developers actually put some time on it, for the price it costs I would rate it next to undertale. Buy this game and you will have a great time C;
